uote><blockquote>信我 搵你d女性朋友出下街<br />\n扮都好忙好充實好開心 佢就會撲返埋嚟</blockquote><br />\n如果係咁咪都係當樓主係兵, 樓主就係想一嘢解決</blockquote><br />\n就算你所講條女當樓主係兵<br />\n到時控制權都係樓主手中 到時樓主可以揀拒絕佢同拖延<br />\n彼此消長下 形勢慢慢傾返去樓主嗰邊</blockquote><br />\n我唔知我係咪好消極，<br />\n但係我唔想再勉強，<br />\n只係想唔記得呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n不過唔知應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪撚咁消極啦ching</blockquote><br />\n其實我之前拍過一次拖，<br />\n不過係因為某d原因而一齊，<br />\n唔係真係鍾意對方。<br />\n雖然我自問有做好作為男朋友既本份<br />\n但我心入面好愧疚。<br />\n<br />\n所以今次可以話係報應<br />\n呢次我想直視返自己既感情，<br />\n唔想再用d tricks去令人鐘意我。<br />\n<br />\n我只係一個人，<br />\n我會因為失戀而唔開心，<br />\n就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc7b79b179adc61308ef9194395cf0eb01251a3","tid":477434,"uid":51561,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T05:30:49.000Z","msg":"做Gym<br />\n做運動<br />\n將意志力磨曬落自己身上<br />\n唔好俾自己停住<br />\n想喊就喊，唔好忍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打你好叻架喇，加油呀"},{"pid":"053ff99bee2b2526f8487efb553b128cc1d9ca6e","tid":477434,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T05:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來啤酒真係好難飲，<br />\n因為我平時唔飲酒<br />\n琴晚想做返個唏噓既真男人<br />\n一野對半打已經Wing wing地，<br />\n之後個頭仲痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過訓醒之後，<br />\n依舊係放唔低，<br />\n究竟點解d人會鍾意飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好柒</blockquote><br />\nSorry 囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/no